  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\nCurrently app just stuck on the same screen in case of syncing / getting error\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n1) Syncing is shown as per design [here](https://www.figma.com/file/V6nlpAWIf2e1XU8RJ9yQPe/Syncing-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=675-179660&mode=design&t=XLVqA7gTpM88imPD-4) \r\n\r\n2) In case of error[]( https://www.figma.com/file/V6nlpAWIf2e1XU8RJ9yQPe/Syncing-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=675-179641&mode=design&t=XLVqA7gTpM88imPD-4) - or at least display an error somehow in a raw format\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nVideo: https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/4557972/649b3f41-629e-4327-9df4-1d5774c0a23a\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1. Try to sync for example devices on different networks\r\n2. Observe the result\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly \r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
